d psychischer Leistung.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 0aMass media and sports. 0aSports journalismxElectronic books. 0aSports journalism. 4aRhetorik. 4aSportberichterstattung. 4aSportjournalismus. 7aLANGUAGE ARTS & DISCIPLINES / Linguistics / General.2bisacsh  aRhetoric.  asports journalism.  asports reporting.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Social Sciences 2000 - 2014z9783110638080oZDB-23-GSS08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2012z9783110288995oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET LINGUISTIK UND LITERATURWISSENSCHAFT  2012z9783110288896oZDB-23-DGA0 cprintz978311027449340uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311027459240uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110274592423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110274592/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LS  aEBA_CL_SN  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGAb2012  aZDB-23-DGGb2012  aZDB-23-GSSc2000d2014